## How Speed Insights Works

The implementation enables automatic performance metric collection for your Vercel deployment:

1. **Automatic Tracking**: When deployed to Vercel, the `SpeedInsights` component automatically tracks Core Web Vitals and other performance metrics
2. **Dashboard Visibility**: Performance data is automatically sent to the Vercel dashboard under the "Speed Insights" tab
3. **Privacy**: Data collection respects user privacy and complies with privacy standards

## Configuration Notes

For your Vite + React setup (classified as "other" or "create-react-app" type in Vercel docs):

- The `SpeedInsights` component is a wrapper around the tracking script that integrates seamlessly with React
- No additional configuration is needed - the component works automatically once deployed to Vercel
- The tracking script endpoint `/_vercel/speed-insights/script.js` will be automatically available after deployment

